review_blob: Fine. Not very much taste, more on the caramally side with a bit of cigarrette butt on the finish. Not really offensive but to be honest, not really anything
beer_name: Big Rock Warthog English Style Mild Ale

review_blob: Kinda like a bud, only very slightly more interesting. Had it in a bottle in ottowa at the ottowa jazz fest
Solid look, and I usually like Brooklyn, but this one falls a little flat. Almondy flavor but kinda falls flat after the initial hit.
Solid ambery look to a nice iPa. A bit of that cigarette butt vibe I get from ipas from time to time.
Solid iPa, not too much bite and goes down easy. Found it easy to drink with milder flavors and it doesnt overwhelm the food.
